Home UCA

Welcome to UCA !

International dimension

   The university is committed to developing educational programmes for an
   international public (dual-award programmes) and to enhancing its
   research at an international level.

Come to UCA

   Your university has an agreement with University of Clermont Auvergne
   and you have been selected for study mobility within the framework of
   an Erasmus, BIC or bilateral exchange programme, here is you all need
   to know about what to do.

Learn French

   The centre FLEURA welcomes foreigners who want to learn French and
   deepen their knowledge of the language and French culture, both in
   regular education or continuing education.

   logo-UCA English version


